data.description: Don't miss out on this lovely updated 3 bedroom all brick Bungalow home ready for a new owner. Move-in ready 3 bedroom, 2 car garage and full basement with a ton of features. Brand new kitchen counter top, updated bathroom, tons of storage, screened-in back porch, garage has a covered patio, new A/C unit, new garage door put in, all appliances and side driveway. All hardwoods will be polished, kitchen floor are being replaced and a couple of doors are being replaced. The walls will be retouched. The full basement has the potential for a fourth bedroom, just add the drywall and a 2nd bath. The basement also has a full bar, ready for your personal updates. Schedule your private tour today!
